        "description": "在无溶剂条件下，使用磷酸铌（NbOPO4）催化剂催化环己酮的自羟醛缩合反应，反应温度160°C，反应时间1-3小时，分别在氮气或氢气气氛（初始压力3.5、5、10 bar）下进行，以生产C12-C18高密度燃料前体分子。",
        "text_snippet": "In this study, a range of high-density fuel precursor molecules with fuel relevant carbon numbers (C12 – C18), have been produced via solvent-free carbon-carbon coupling of cyclohexanone as a model lignin-derived ketone using low-cost niobium phosphate (NbOPO4) catalyst. In the experiments, niobium phosphate (NbOPO4) at 160 ◦C with 1–3 h reaction times, was used under nitrogen or hydrogen atmospheres.",
